# 🛒 CloudShop

CloudShop is a modern **online shopping website** designed to provide a seamless and secure e-commerce experience. It allows users to browse products, add items to the cart, and make purchases with ease. The project focuses on a responsive design, smooth navigation, and efficient backend operations.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🏠 **Home Page** – Showcases featured and trending products  
- 🔍 **Product Search & Filter** – Easily find products by category or keyword  
- 🛍️ **Product Details Page** – View detailed information about each product  
- 🛒 **Shopping Cart** – Add, remove, or update items in the cart  
- 💳 **Checkout System** – Place orders securely and efficiently  
- 🔐 **User Authentication** – Sign up, login, and manage user accounts  
- ⚙️ **Admin Dashboard** – Manage products, categories, and orders (optional)  
- 📱 **Responsive Design** – Works smoothly on all devices  

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

**Frontend:** React.js, HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Bootstrap / Tailwind CSS  
**Backend:** Node.js, Express.js  
**Database:** MongoDB (Mongoose)  
**Authentication:** JWT (JSON Web Token)  
**Version Control:** Git & GitHub  
**Deployment:** Vercel / Render / Netlify  

